{"tid":694870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發！】皇馬主動給C朗加薪！","createTime":"2018-06-08T17:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T07:27:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":67,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"76d97b2080ae9f79fd0f56d04122fb0073ce79f5","tid":694870,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"侮辱性加薪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 皇馬逼C朗走人<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《馬卡報》以頭版形式報道，皇家馬德里主席皮里茲唔願意為C朗大幅度加薪，開出嘅新合約年薪只係加咗400萬歐元，消息話佢呢次侮辱性加人工，目的係逼C朗同佢反面，等對方開口嗌走人。 <br />\n<br />\n據講皇馬打算將C朗嘅除稅後2,100萬歐元年薪，提高到2,500萬歐元，計埋贏冠軍嘅獎金至有機會到達3,000萬歐元，比起C朗要求嘅3,700萬歐元年薪差好遠，要知道美斯有4,000萬歐元年薪，尼馬有3,700萬歐元年薪，睇怕C朗知道後真係會扯晒火。"},{"pid":"3a4841539012eef31e785ec20da712cc0138a312","tid":694870,"uid":50595,"like":78,"dislike":13,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"貴庚啊，想攞3000萬"},{"pid":"fb2e1c3e5ff79cf13ccb720edbe4f9bc20b3ddea","tid":694870,"uid":99700,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"快點侮辱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6703f2345eb89c6e0dfb4a3fbb1aaa17d045ef","tid":694870,"uid":15376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"執到喇 33歲仲有人工加"},{"pid":"fe85cff742c6fdecff3f4273f77aa147ef8019cc","tid":694870,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5624ca43d030c707355bf2e0641c814ae37a8f","tid":694870,"uid":130419,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"年年都話走 搞到今年少左好多人關注 <br />\n個個都以為佢吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c1f270b5934746b27166967cd822bb51bd9dc7","tid":694870,"uid":12628,"like":2